title: Sample Book
inscribed: Stamped on inside of front cover: H.A. Elsberg 51 East 57th St. New York
creditline: Gift of the Estate of Herman A. Elsberg
description: Sample book with paper leaves bound in grey cloth covers. Pasted on the paper leaves are about 400 samples of silks and cottons, in plain and patterned weaves, some with printed designs and some brocaded.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book; paper, silk, cotton; H x W: 35.5 × 26 cm (14 in. × 10 1/4 in.); Gift of the Estate of Herman A. Elsberg; 1941-35-1
